    "Potential integration of ethical and legal constraints (e.g., insider trading regulations).",
    "(4) Human Alignment.",
    "Large language models can inadvertently propagate harmful behaviors-e.g., misinformation, social biases, or privacy violations.",
    "In finance, these concerns become critical due to the potential for disinformation (fake financial news), toxic content (harassment in investor forums), or privacy breaches in sensitive customer data.",
